## Definitions

For the purposes of this license:

"FORKING" means adding your own customizations when (optionally) forking this project on GitHub, and distributing those customizations. Customizations include changes to the source code but exclude configurations.

"REDISTRIBUTION" means distributing the source code of this project, any source code dependent on this project, excluding the loadstring (a single line of code that fetches this GitHub project and initializes it), and any configurations.

